===Etymology===
From {{ME.}} '''persone''' < {{OF.}} '''[[persone]]''' (human being, French [[personne]]) < {{L.}} '''[[persona]]''' (a dramatic ''mask'', hence ''role, part, character''), possibly < Etruscan '''[[phersu]]''' ("mask").

